Project Bureau — ATF1502AS Logic Block A Macrocells

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress. See more in the repository

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block A uses 320 (known) fuses within range 15360..16320 for macrocells MC1, MC2, MC3, MC4, MC5, MC6, MC7, MC8, MC9, MC10, MC11, MC12, MC13, MC14, MC15, MC16.
